					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/ralliston-s-authorpage</guid>
				<title>Ralliston&#039;s Authorpage</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/ralliston-s-authorpage</link>
				<description>


&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: right;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt;Ralliston&#039;s Authorpage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If by any chance you clicked the link to this page, it probably means you read one of my articles. How about you learn who I am then? I&#039;m &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ralliston&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5986843&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610224182&quot; alt=&quot;Ralliston&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5986843)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ralliston&quot;  &gt;Ralliston&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;footnoteref-4506-1&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot; class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;  &gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;, an amateur writer and a Junior Staff member of the Collections Team and Introductions Subteam of the Community Outreach Team on the SCP Wiki.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&#039;m a very proud owner of two of the bestest girls, Fiffy and Franny&lt;sup class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;footnoteref-4506-2&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot; class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;  &gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; (of Fifka and Franka, as dog names don&#039;t translate well), a giant science-nerd, and an unhealthy fan of Queen and David Bowie. I&#039;ve been a book worm and a piano player since I can really remember, and as you might see, my writing is inspired by different books by a long shot. I don&#039;t really write a lot of memorable things here, but hopefully if I keep my pace I&#039;ll write something people will talk about some time in the future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more personal stuff if you want to know that for some reason, I&#039;m 18, I come from Poland and go by he/him. Small trivia you&#039;ll probably not care much for, I&#039;m the guy who suggested the &amp;quot;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/system:page-tags/tag/nameless#pages&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;nameless&lt;/a&gt;&amp;quot; tag and who made the &amp;quot;Secret Christmas Presents&amp;quot; &lt;a href=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-achievement-badges&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Achievement Badge&lt;/a&gt;. It&#039;s not like it matters, but that&#039;s something to think about. Without further ado though, let&#039;s actually get to the contents of this page, shall we?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpper.com/user/5986843&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/ralliston-s-authorpage/scplogo/medium.jpg&quot; width=&quot;45&quot; alt=&quot;scplogo&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-achievement-badges/Attendance.png&quot; alt=&quot;Attendance.png&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-achievement-badges/Orange.png&quot; alt=&quot;Orange.png&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-achievement-badges/Arrows.png&quot; alt=&quot;Arrows.png&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-achievement-badges/Scream.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Scream.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-achievement-badges/Hearts.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Hearts.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-achievement-badges/Media.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Media.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-achievement-badges/TV.png&quot; alt=&quot;TV.png&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-achievement-badges/Cycle.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Cycle.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-achievement-badges/Apple.png&quot; alt=&quot;Apple.png&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/ralliston-s-authorpage/gift.png&quot; alt=&quot;gift.png&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-achievement-badges/Ducky.png&quot; alt=&quot;Ducky.png&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;footnoteref-4506-3&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot; class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;  &gt;3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/Ralliston1&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.colorbook.io/img/icons/socialmedia/twitter.svg&quot; width=&quot;38&quot; alt=&quot;twitter.svg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;wiki-tabview-daef382e65e82a7bfe04a198b1de1c48&quot; class=&quot;yui-navset&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;yui-nav&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;selected&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;SCPs&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Tales&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;GoI Formats&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Other Stuff&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;yui-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;wiki-tab-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float: center; border: solid 4px #BB0011; width: auto; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top:1em; margin-bottom:1em; box-shadow: 2px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-folded&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;►&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded-link&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;▼&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is easily the dumbest thing I have so far written&lt;sup class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;footnoteref-4506-4&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot; class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;  &gt;4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;. It started off as an inside joke between &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6030962&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610224182&quot; alt=&quot;Veralta&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6030962)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta&quot;  &gt;Veralta&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jakob17&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5884163&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610224182&quot; alt=&quot;Jakob17&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5884163)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jakob17&quot;  &gt;Jakob17&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, and myself on the SCPD Discord Server, and whilst the stupidity of it was beyond anything I&#039;ve ever read, I genuinely couldn&#039;t resist the urge to write it. The article blew up into +40 within the first day, being my first thing to get into the &amp;quot;big numbers&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float: center; border: solid 4px #BB0011; width: auto; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top:1em; margin-bottom:1em; box-shadow: 2px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-folded&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;►&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded-link&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;▼&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A rewrite of my first proper SCP ever, SCP-5555-EX. I wrote 0000-EX in approximately one day upon being hit with inspiration for a rewrite I&#039;ve been meaning to do for a long time. Though I&#039;m pretty happy with how this article has turned out, I am probably going to rewrite it for a third time. We&#039;ll see.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float: center; border: solid 4px #BB0011; width: auto; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top:1em; margin-bottom:1em; box-shadow: 2px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-folded&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;►&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded-link&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;▼&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first installment of the Ontokinetics Saga. I started writing this after me and my mother were riding through a section of our town that was totally abandoned - the buildings were almost intact, yet not a single human being could be found there. Additionally, the whole place was covered in fog, which only added to the already existing spookiness of it. My imagination did the rest of course, with me quickly tying the idea to an overarching narrative I had in my mind for quite some time, and thus SCP-5936 was born.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float: center; border: solid 4px #BB0011; width: auto; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top:1em; margin-bottom:1em; box-shadow: 2px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-folded&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;►&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded-link&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;▼&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A long time ago I said on SCPD that if &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5464&quot;&gt;SCP-5464&lt;/a&gt; somehow reaches +100, I will write something whilst drunk, similarly to what &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610224182&quot; alt=&quot;PeppersGhost&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost&quot;  &gt;PeppersGhost&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; did with &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3943&quot;&gt;SCP-3943&lt;/a&gt; after winning the SCP-4000 Contest. People only encouraged me of course. However, since I had no such beverages at my disposal, I thought that sleep deprivation is a good substitute. This is the product of that challenge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float: center; border: solid 4px #BB0011; width: auto; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top:1em; margin-bottom:1em; box-shadow: 2px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-folded&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;►&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded-link&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;▼&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This article is a rewrite of a very old draft of mine modified to fir both my current standards and the storyline already established in &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5936&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;SCP-5936&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scp-wiki.wikidot.com/critter-profile-sparky&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Critter Profile: Sparky!&lt;/a&gt;. I had tons of fun writing this one, and I&#039;m very happy with the end result. I think it&#039;s obvious by now, but I love serialized narratives strung out in-between different articles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;wiki-tab-0-1&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float: center; border: solid 4px #BB0011; width: auto; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top:1em; margin-bottom:1em; box-shadow: 2px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-folded&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;►&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded-link&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;▼&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whilst before The Watchman I did attempt to write an article once&lt;sup class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;footnoteref-4506-5&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot; class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;  &gt;5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;, this was my first successful one. As I had no idea what I was doing back in the day, I coldposted it, and surprisingly enough, it survived, and currently sits at a pretty nice number of upvotes. The whole idea and layout for the article pretty much popped into my mind during a walk near a sea and I wrote the whole thing in approximately 30 minutes. It&#039;s still, to this day, one of my favorite works of mine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float: center; border: solid 4px #BB0011; width: auto; padding: 1px 15px; margin: auto; margin-top:1em; margin-bottom:1em; box-shadow: 2px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-folded&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;►&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded-link&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;▼&amp;nbsp;Author&amp;nbsp;commentary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The second installment in my short &amp;quot;series&amp;quot; centered around the world of the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/revised-entry&quot;&gt;Revised Entry&lt;/a&gt; of SCP-173. Though looking back, it&#039;s pretty mediocre, I still like it quite the bit - especially considering that this was the first article my author avatar, Daniel Asheworth, appeared in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
