&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&#039;ve had a ton of fun writing this one. I think I wrote it exactly one day after getting the info about my recipient - from doing the art to the writing, it was an absolute blast. Hopefully &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/general-goose&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6534493&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610224182&quot; alt=&quot;General Goose&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6534493)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/general-goose&quot;  &gt;General Goose&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; has as much fun reading it as I had creating it.&lt;/p&gt;
