&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;It&#039;s Now &amp;amp; Never: a reverie endeavor&lt;br /&gt;
Awaits somnambulant directives&lt;br /&gt;
To take the helm.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Believe me, darling:&lt;br /&gt;
The stars were made for falling!&lt;br /&gt;
Like melting obelisks as tall as another realm.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;[&amp;#8230;]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Joy mirage&#039;s kingdom come, no one left at stake.&lt;br /&gt;
Now that existence is on the wake,&lt;br /&gt;
Let&#039;s see what we can make.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
