&lt;div class=&quot;heading&quot;&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt;Who I Am&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hello.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My name&#039;s &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610224182&quot; alt=&quot;Nagiros&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros&quot;  &gt;Nagiros&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, although I also use Nagi for short. I use she/they pronouns, and I&#039;m currently 19. I&#039;m a believer in music and emotion. I&#039;ve got a lot to learn about this site and life in general.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I review articles posted to the Idea and Draft forums, as well as creating my own SCPs, tales, and GOI Formats — you may see me around sometimes, and I&#039;m always happy to help if you want some eyes on a draft.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&#039;m most well-known for making a lot of contributions to the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/site-17-hub&quot;&gt;Site-17 Deepwell Catalog&lt;/a&gt; and creating/maintaining the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/esoteric-classes-complete-list&quot;&gt;Comprehensive List of Esoteric Classes&lt;/a&gt;. I have aspirations of doing more — I want to be prolific and have a formidable backlog of content I can be proud of. I want to inspire others.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#039;ll see.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;heading&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 75px;&quot;&gt;
