					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"></div> <blockquote> <p><em>It's Now &amp; Never: a reverie endeavor<br /> Awaits somnambulant directives<br /> To take the helm.</em></p> <p><em>Believe me, darling:<br /> The stars were made for falling!<br /> Like melting obelisks as tall as another realm.</em></p> <p>[&#8230;]</p> <p><em>Joy mirage's kingdom come, no one left at stake.<br /> Now that existence is on the wake,<br /> Let's see what we can make.</em></p> <div style="text-align: right;"> <p><strong>— ミラクルミュージカル's <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://youtu.be/uxyM7vhU0uU">Dream Sweet in Sea Major</a></span></strong></p> </div> </blockquote> <table style="background: black; width: 100%; border-spacing: 4px; margin: 50px 0 75px 0"> <tr> <td style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 200%; width: 25%; background: #2e2e2e; text-shadow: 0px 0px 4px black; padding: 0 10px;" rowspan="3"> <h1><span><a href="https://youtu.be/4Hg1Kudd_x4">♫</a></span></h1> </td> <td style="text-align: center; veritcal-align: middle; width: 75%; background: #383838; text-shadow: 0px 0px 4px black; padding: 0 10px;"> <h1><span><a href="http://nagiros.wikidot.com">Personal Site 🦀</a></span></h1> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="text-align: center; veritcal-align: middle; width: 75%; background: #383838; text-shadow: 0px 0px 4px black; padding: 0 10px;"> <h1><span><a href="https://twitter.com/Nagiros1">@Nagiros1 🐦</a></span></h1> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="text-align: center; veritcal-align: middle; width: 75%; background: #383838; text-shadow: 0px 0px 4px black; padding: 0 10px;"> <h1><span><a href="http://scpper.com/user/4665703">SCPper Record 📈</a></span></h1> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="text-align: center; veritcal-align: middle; width: 75%; background: #383838; text-shadow: 0px 0px 4px black; padding: 0 10px;" colspan="2"> <h1><span>Avatar by <a href="https://www.deviantart.com/guweiz/art/Chill-745214892">GUWEIZ</a> 🧙‍♀️</span></h1> </td> </tr> </table> <div class="heading"> <h1><span>Who I Am</span></h1> </div> <p>Hello.</p> <p>My name's <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224182" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" >Nagiros</a></span>, although I also use Nagi for short. I use she/they pronouns, and I'm currently 19. I'm a believer in music and emotion. I've got a lot to learn about this site and life in general.</p> <p>I review articles posted to the Idea and Draft forums, as well as creating my own SCPs, tales, and GOI Formats — you may see me around sometimes, and I'm always happy to help if you want some eyes on a draft.</p> <p>I'm most well-known for making a lot of contributions to the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/site-17-hub">Site-17 Deepwell Catalog</a> and creating/maintaining the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/esoteric-classes-complete-list">Comprehensive List of Esoteric Classes</a>. I have aspirations of doing more — I want to be prolific and have a formidable backlog of content I can be proud of. I want to inspire others.</p> <p>We'll see.</p> <div class="heading" style="margin-top: 75px;"> <h1><span>What I've Done</span></h1> </div> <div class="heading"> <h1><span>Reflection</span></h1> </div> <div id="wiki-tabview-087245f813277dbacf2b6ed992a133db" class="yui-navset"> <ul class="yui-nav"> <li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>Author Commentary</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>Achievements</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>Control Panel</em></a></li> </ul> <div class="yui-content"> <div id="wiki-tab-0-0"> <h1><span>SCP-4051</span></h1> <p>Well, here we are. First SCP. The one that started the Deepwell Catalog, even if that wasn't my intent when I posted it. I'm still surprised people liked it.</p> <p>4051 is… complex. It's a story about a teenage vigilante superhero who joins a task force and unlocks a hidden power by the end — and it's all played straight. I had no aspiration of commenting on well-known tropes which have been known to kill articles on this site. I just wanted to write a story despite them.</p> <p>4051 was a cry for help. The Nagiros who posted it was trapped in a hostile setting, tormented by authority figures who should have been looking after her, stuck in a mindspace of passive acceptance and denial.</p> <p>I've had a lot of requests to continue Rainer's story. As I've grown as a person, he's remained at the sidelines: foraying with <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4260">Death</a>, finding some <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4415">friends</a>, inspiring <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/systems-patch">revolution</a>. I'd like to continue that story.</p> <h1><span>SCP-4175</span></h1> <p>I wrote this for Pride Month of 2019 and it's currently my most popular article. Personally? I don't think it's my best work.</p> <p>Then again, a lot of people liked it. I know a lot of readers were excited to see the trans pride flag on a featured article — even if it did bring a fair amount of controversy my way.</p> <h1><span>AFTERLIFE OPHIDIAN /// The Foundation Over Heaven</span></h1> <p>A poetry-prose piece based in despair. I felt trapped in life, faced by oblivion on all sides, and channeled it into this article.</p> <p>It exists, I suppose.</p> <h1><span>SCP-4755</span></h1> <p>Now then, it looks like my pet anomalous science, essophysics, has finally come into its own. The Foundation's tasted the blood in the water and they aren't backing down. If the universe rejects them, then the solution is simple: build a better universe.</p> <p>Expect great things in the future.</p> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-1" style="display:none"> <div class="heading" style="margin: auto 10px"> <h1><span>Accomplishments</span></h1> </div> <table class="wiki-content-table"> <tr> <th>Criteria</th> <th>Date Achieved</th> </tr> <tr> <td>Have three works in the first page of the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/top-rated-pages-this-month">Top Rated New Pages</a> at once.</td> <td>January 1, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have an SCP reach +50 votes.</td> <td>January 21, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have an SCP reach +75 votes.</td> <td>March 12, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have a tale reach +50 votes.</td> <td>March 14, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have an SCP reach +100 votes.</td> <td>April 20, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write five works.</td> <td>May 5, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have a tale reach +75 votes.</td> <td>June 17, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have an article featured one time.</td> <td>August 1, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have an SCP reach +150 votes.</td> <td>August 29, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have a tale reach +100 votes.</td> <td>November 7, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write ten works.</td> <td>November 11, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write five tales.</td> <td>November 11, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have an SCP reach +200 votes.</td> <td>December 5, 2019</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write five SCPs.</td> <td>December 16, 2020</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have an article featured two times.</td> <td>January 10, 2020</td> </tr> </table> <div class="heading" style="margin: 50px 10px 0 10px"> <h1><span>Goals</span></h1> </div> <table class="wiki-content-table"> <tr> <th>Criteria</th> </tr> <tr> <td>Have three SCPs in the first page of the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/top-rated-pages-this-month">Top Rated New Pages</a> at once.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have three tales in the first page of the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/top-rated-pages-this-month">Top Rated New Pages</a> at once.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have four works on the first page of the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/top-rated-pages-this-month">Top Rated New Pages</a> at once.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have four SCPs on the first page of the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/top-rated-pages-this-month">Top Rated New Pages</a> at once.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have four tales in the first page of the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/top-rated-pages-this-month">Top Rated New Pages</a> at once.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have five works on the first page of the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/top-rated-pages-this-month">Top Rated New Pages</a> at once.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have five SCPs on the first page of the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/top-rated-pages-this-month">Top Rated New Pages</a> at once.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have five tales in the first page of the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/top-rated-pages-this-month">Top Rated New Pages</a> at once.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have a tale reach +150 votes.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have a tale reach +200 votes.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Have an article featured three times.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write ten SCPs.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write ten tales.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write twenty works.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write twenty SCPs.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write twenty tales.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write fifty works.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write fifty SCPs.</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Write fifty tales.</td> </tr> </table> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-2" style="display:none"> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h2><span>All page I've created.</span></h2> </div> <hr /> <p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/workbench:tags">✨ Tag Workbench ✨</a></strong></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="heading" style="margin-top: 75px;"> <h1><span>Custodianship</span></h1> </div> <p>In the event that I become unresponsive/unreachable for three weeks or more, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/voidlady" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5366711&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224182" alt="VoidLady" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5366711)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/voidlady" >VoidLady</a></span> becomes the caretaker of all my