ody"> <div class="feature-title"> <p><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5109">SCP-5109: The One-Time Password</a></p> </div> <div class="feature-subtitle"> <p>by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" >HarryBlank</a></span></p> </div> <p><em>SCP-5109 must not be spoken. This restriction is waived in the event of an imminent threat to the life of its keeper&#8230;</em></p> </div> <div class="panel-footer"> <p><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/canon-renaissance-contest">CanonCon Prize Feature</a></p> </div> </div> <div class="content-panel left-column"> <div class="panel-heading"> <p>Reviewers' Spotlight: Nagiros</p> </div> <div class="panel-body"> <div class="feature-title"> <p><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5699">SCP-5699: Take Care of Yourself.</a></p> </div> <div class="feature-subtitle"> <p>by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/amelia-wright" >Amelia Wright</a></span></p> </div> <p><em>As such, the O5 Council have ruled that SCP-5699 does not require active containment.</em></p> </div> <div class="panel-footer"> <p><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/reviewers-spotlight-archive">Reviewers' Spotlight Archive</a></p> </div> </div> <div class="content-panel right-column"> <div class="panel-heading"> <p>Reviewers' Spotlight: Quadraginta</p> </div> <div class="panel-body"> <div class="feature-title"> <p><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5266">SCP-5266: IDIOT SUCCUMBS TO NEUROTOXIN WHILE LISTENING TO MACHO MAN CLICK NOW TO SEE</a></p> </div> <div class="feature-subtitle"> <p>by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iamtheooga" >IAmTheOoga</a></span></p> </div> <p><em>Object Class: Keter</em></p> </div> <div class="panel-footer"> <p><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/reviewers-spotlight-archive">Reviewers' Spotlight Archive</a></p> </div> </div> </div> <div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div> <div class="news-block content-panel"> <div class="panel-heading