												<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This archive displays all works that have been featured on the site’s front page as part of the Reviewers’ Spotlight, which acknowledges the time and effort spent by forum reviewers helping other authors develop and edit and their works for the mainsite.</p> <p>Each month, community members are encouraged to nominate forum reviewers who have been both particularly helpful and active. Members of the Forum Criticism Team will then discuss the nominations, and select four prominent reviewers to choose the month’s Reviewers’ Spotlight front-page features.</p> <p>Nominations and recommendations and should be sent via wikidot message to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span> (team captain of Forum Crit).</p> <hr /> <p>Double Reviewers’ Spotlight features this month due to contest prize feature schedule!</p> <p><strong>1 January 2021 - selected by <em>TheAlienBaby</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4333">SCP-4333</a> (The Profligate) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" >CadaverCommander</a></span></li> </ul> <p><strong>1 January 2021 - selected by <em>cybersqyd</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/penny-for-your-thoughts">Penny for Your Thoughts?</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4057128&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Alces_alces" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4057128)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" >Alces_alces</a></span></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 January 2021 - selected by <em>Nagiros</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5699">SCP-5699</a> (Take Care of Yourself.) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/amelia-wright" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3754950&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Amelia Wright" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3754950)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/amelia-wright" >Amelia Wright</a></span></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 January 2021 - selected by <em>Quadraginta</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5266">SCP-5266</a> (IDIOT SUCCUMBS TO NEUROTOXIN WHILE LISTENING TO MACHO MAN CLICK NOW TO SEE) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iamtheooga" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3942052&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="IAmTheOoga" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3942052)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iamtheooga" >IAmTheOoga</a></span></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 January 2021 - selected by <em>RockTeethMothEyes</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: Wait and see!</li> </ul> <p><strong>17 January 2021 - selected by <em>Grigori Karpin</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: Wait and see!</li> </ul> <p><strong>25 January 2021 - selected by <em>EthanHansen</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: Wait and see!</li> </ul> <p><strong>25 January 2021 - selected by <em>Sonderance</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: Wait and see!</li> </ul> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2019&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;JANUARY&nbsp;-&nbsp;APRIL</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2019&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;JANUARY&nbsp;-&nbsp;APRIL</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">January 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 January 2019 - selected by <em>scpcrnp</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4164">SCP-4164</a> (The Universal Instruction Manual) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/literallymechanical" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2829014&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="LiterallyMechanical" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2829014)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/literallymechanical" >LiterallyMechanical</a></span></li> <li><em>These instructions invariably fail to follow the standard operating procedures intended by the device's manufacturer, but rather direct an operator to use the device in an unsafe manner.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 January 2019 - selected by <em>Shanor</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4999">SCP-4999</a> (Someone to Watch Over Us) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" >CadaverCommander</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4999 has not been seen to engage in any other activity or behavior, and demanifests immediately upon the subject's death.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 January 2019 - selected by <em>MathBrush</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/introductory-antimemetics">Introductory Antimemetics</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=571081&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="qntm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=571081)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" >qntm</a></span></li> <li><em>“You must know how that intro goes. It's like an atom bomb to the ego. I just had almost everything I know overturned.”</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 January 2019 - selected by <em>Reverend Fox</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3431">SCP-3431</a> (Refuse Koala) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span></li> <li><em>All personnel regularly involved with caring for koalas are to be told to never take any food offered by koalas, and to remind guests to do the same.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">February 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 February 2019 - selected by <em>Pedantique</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/maim-the-sky-slay-the-sun-hub">Maim the Sky, Slay the Sun Hub</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedantique" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3118444&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Pedantique" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3118444)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedantique" >Pedantique</a></span></li> <li><em>Fire was stolen from the gods. Symbolically, literally, or something in between?</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 February 2019 - selected by <em>Laneous</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4378">SCP-4378</a> (Her Noodly Appendage) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404096&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Woedenaz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404096)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" >Woedenaz</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4378 is a single uncooked De Cecco-brand lasagna noodle.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 February 2019 - selected by <em>RockTeethMothEyes</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3367">SCP-3367</a> (Prayers from Children, Eternally Answered) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1345012&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="kinchtheknifeblade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1345012)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" >kinchtheknifeblade</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-3367 is a Level 5 Ecto-geographical site, marked by its consistently changing layout, non-Euclidean spaces, and sentience.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>24 February 2019 - selected by <em>psul</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/on-mount-golgotha-hub">On Mount Golgotha Hub</a> by multiple authors</li> <li><em>&quot;I was born with music inside me. Music was one of my parts. Like my ribs, my kidneys, my liver, my heart. Like my blood.&quot;</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">March 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 March 2019 - selected by <em>Polynom</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4144">SCP-4144</a> (The Most Important Meal Of The Day) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1705184&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Mortos" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1705184)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" >Mortos</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4144 is the concept of breakfast.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 March 2019 - selected by <em>DrChandra</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/the-den-of-disquiet">The Den of Disquiet</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayoculpa" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3489662&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="mayoculpa" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3489662)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayoculpa" >mayoculpa</a></span></li> <li><em>The mind called Herman Portunus Fuller was a burning tightrope, a taut thread strung across an ocean of suffering flesh, silence shredding in its grip.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 March 2019 - selected by <em>Ayers</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4601">SCP-4601</a> (No, It Is the Corpses That Are Wrong) by <span class="error-inline"><em>KindlyTurtleClem</em> does not match any existing user name</span></li> <li><em>SCP-4601 is a headless humanoid measuring 1.5m tall with vestigial limbs attached to adjacent sockets on the torso utilizing hot-glue, duct-tape, and threaded bolts.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 March 2019 - selected by <em>DrCaroll</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4616">SCP-4616</a> (It Haunts The Fields) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" >DrChandra</a></span></li> <li><em>During daylight hours, SCP-4616 appearances are rare and sporadic, mostly limited to appearing at the edge of the wooded area.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">April 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 April 2019 - selected by <em>TheMightyMcB</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3741">SCP-3741</a> (The World Is Your Oyster) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" >TheMightyMcB</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-3741 is a phenomenon that is currently exhibited by 29 eastern oysters, but may extend to a small quantity of wild oysters.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 April 2019 - selected by <em>ihp</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2589">SCP-2589</a> (Don't Leave Me This Way) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/faminepulse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4275444&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="faminepulse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4275444)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/faminepulse" >faminepulse</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-2589 only physically consumed an individual if it was assisted.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 April 2019 - selected by <em>Crashington</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1193">SCP-1193</a> (Buried Giant) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ophite" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=354957&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="ophite" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=354957)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ophite" >ophite</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-1193-01 is a genetically normal human arm of unusual length, located in a drainage pipe inside the basement of a telephone switching station in Scottsdale, Arizona.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 April 2019 - selected by <em>Schumacher</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3758">SCP-3758</a> (The Last Dodo) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/daveyoufool" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2034230&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="daveyoufool" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2034230)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/daveyoufool" >daveyoufool</a></span></li> <li><em>Due to the fact that SCP-3758-B emits 12,000 roentgens per hour of ionizing radiation from its skin, exact measurements have proven impractical.</em></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <p>~</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2019&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;MAY&nbsp;-&nbsp;AUGUST</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2019&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;MAY&nbsp;-&nbsp;AUGUST</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">May 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 May 2019 - selected by <em>qntm</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3454">SCP-3454</a> (<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">The Land</span> <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em>DENIERS</em></span></strong> of Tall Bees) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tl333s" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1304786&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="TL333s" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1304786)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tl333s" >TL333s</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-3454 is the designation for individuals who don't agree that the bees are tall.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 May 2019 - selected by <em>Gabriel Jade</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4522">SCP-4522</a> (The Mystical Village of the Jade Peach) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404096&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Woedenaz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404096)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" >Woedenaz</a></span></li> <li><em>Grasp this offering between both hands. Feel its weight both in hand as well as in self. Know that which is displayed will tell all that I need to know.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 May 2019 - selected by <em>RockTeethMothEyes</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3721">SCP-3721</a> (Obsolete Weapons System) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="UraniumEmpire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" >UraniumEmpire</a></span></li> <li><em>“I can still feel it, though. I'm constantly fucking angry. Every single second I spend cooped in this fucking machine, you know what I'm thinking about?”</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 May 2019 - selected by <em>calamitous1</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3007">SCP-3007</a> (World of Two Artists) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2938475&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Zhange" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2938475)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" >Zhange</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-3007-1 is a reoccurring hallucinogenic phenomenon, with no apparent pattern regarding age, gender, race, health or occupation.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">June 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 June 2019 - selected by <em>aismallard</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4985">SCP-4985</a> (High Finance) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modernmajorgeneral" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=274283&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="ModernMajorGeneral" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=274283)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modernmajorgeneral" >ModernMajorGeneral</a></span></li> <li><em>As a result, the operation of SCP-4985 approximates that of a European monarchy of the Late Middle Ages.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 June 2019 - selected by <em>Crashington</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4958">SCP-4958</a> (You Are Loved) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4463776&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="N_Aepic_Fael" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4463776)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" >N_Aepic_Fael</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4958 refers to Lycoris radiata (more commonly known as red spider lilies) that bloom near individuals who have had a major conflict with their loved ones.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 June 2019 - selected by <em>N_Aepic_Fael</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4064">SCP-4064</a> (&quot;It's not you, it's us&quot;) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5190300&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Henzoid" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5190300)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" >Henzoid</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4064 is a hive-mind, capable of inhabiting six distinct bodies.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 June 2019 - selected by <em>unclenicolini</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4981">SCP-4981</a> (The Room You Used To Live In) by <span class="error-inline"><em>KindlyTurtleClem</em> does not match any existing user name</span></li> <li><em>MTF Gamma-76 (&quot;Mother Mara&quot;) currently guards the entrance to SCP-4981-B's rental apartment, disguised as custodial staff.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">July 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 July 2019 - selected by <em>wishun</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1169">SCP-1169</a> (Lamarck's Giraffe) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wishun" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1204404&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="wishun" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1204404)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wishun" >wishun</a></span></li> <li><em>Assignment preference will be given to staff who are irreversibly infertile.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 July 2019 - selected by <em>DrSevere</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3844">SCP-3844</a> (To Slay A Dragon) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span></li> <li><em>A dragon. There was a dragon in the mountains. And it looked just like we'd imagined.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 July 2019 - selected by <em>RockTeethMothEyes</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3881">SCP-3881</a> (A Disregarded Proposal) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Ayers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" >Ayers</a></span></li> <li><em>When worn by a human being, SCP-3881 will immediately transport the wearer to an unknown location.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 July 2019 - selected by <em>Zachary Maxwell</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/you-never-visit-anymore">You Never Visit Me Anymore</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zachary-maxwell" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2975899&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Zachary Maxwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2975899)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zachary-maxwell" >Zachary Maxwell</a></span></li> <li><em>She pushed page after page into my hands, always littered with notes and lines under words, in red Sharpie.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">August 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 August 2019 - selected by <em>AKFrost</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4597">SCP-4597</a> (Thick-Skinned Man) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4597's skin possesses accelerated, if flawed, regenerative properties.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 August 2019 - selected by <em>tupacofficial</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4853">SCP-4853</a> (&amp;SCP-4853) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4598089&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="aismallard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4598089)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" >aismallard</a></span></li> <li><em>Other references to SCP-4853 may exist only in this document, and may not exceed ten instances.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 August 2019 - selected by <em>Gee0765</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4954">SCP-4954</a> (Long Live the Tinsmith!) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nameless-mediocre" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4176498&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Nameless Mediocre" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4176498)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nameless-mediocre" >Nameless Mediocre</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4954 is a series of self-replicating satellites, currently ████ in number, that subsist off of orbital debris…</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 August 2019 - selected by <em>Ayers</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4279">SCP-4279</a> (A Toast to my Finished Thesis) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nameless-mediocre" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4176498&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Nameless Mediocre" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4176498)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nameless-mediocre" >Nameless Mediocre</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4279 uses electrical power to generate and assemble matter into theoretically any molecular or atomic form…</em></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <p>~</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2019&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;SEPTEMBER&nbsp;-&nbsp;DECEMBER</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2019&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;SEPTEMBER&nbsp;-&nbsp;DECEMBER</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">September 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 September 2019 - selected by <em>cybersqyd</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/cuteness-on-main">Cuteness On Main!</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ellie3" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3656445&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Ellie3" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3656445)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ellie3" >Ellie3</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4894577&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Laneous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4894577)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" >Laneous</a></span></li> <li><em>Found something utterly unnatural— yet still adorable? Post about it here!</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 September 2019 - selected by <em>N_Aepic_Fael</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/mother-who-demands-ones-toes">Karcist Halyna Ieva, or The Mother Who Demands One's Toes</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4463776&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="N_Aepic_Fael" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4463776)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" >N_Aepic_Fael</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" >TheMightyMcB</a></span></li> <li><em>Where her legs would be instead lies a writhing mass of tumorous blackened tentacles.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 September 2019 - selected by <em>PrLosash</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4465">SCP-4465</a> (No Man is an Island) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span></li> <li><em>Arnold Dubar was 3,000 kilometers away from the nearest victim.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 September 2019 - selected by <em>RockTeethMothEyes</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4294">SCP-4294</a> (In the Cold Shadow of her Ovary Tower) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Gabriel Jade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" >Gabriel Jade</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4294 is perpetually surrounded by a severe snowstorm with wind speeds in excess of 130km/h.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">October 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 October 2019 - selected by <em>MacWarren</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4436">SCP-4436</a> (Jesus Saves) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/spikebrennan" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=908688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="spikebrennan" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=908688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/spikebrennan" >spikebrennan</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4436 is an large active distributed database, presently stored in an array of supercomputers located at Site-48.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 October 2019 - selected by <em>gee0765</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4389-j">SCP-4389-J</a> (Can the Foundation do THIS?) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gee0765" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5376871&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="gee0765" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5376871)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gee0765" >gee0765</a></span></li> <li><em>The anomalous effect of SCP-4389-J varies in potency depending on how long a member of personnel has been employed at the Foundation.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 October 2019 - selected by <em>DrAkimoto</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4795">SCP-4795</a> (Feathered F(r)iends) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mew-ltiverse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5271378&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Mew-ltiverse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5271378)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mew-ltiverse" >Mew-ltiverse</a></span></li> <li><em>A large flock of an estimated 30,000 pigeons had amassed above the park and attacked.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 October 2019 - selected by <em>Tanhony</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4866">SCP-4866</a> (<em>𝘔𝘶𝘳𝘥𝘦𝘳𝘦𝘳</em>™, a product of Optimark Synthetic Personnel Solutions) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" >CadaverCommander</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4866 is a series of murderous synthetic humanoid constructs explicitly advertised as a commercial product, to be sold and purchased by the consumer public.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">November 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 November 2019 - selected by <em>Kybard</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4361">SCP-4361</a> (Red is Her Favorite Color) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kybard" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5717239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Kybard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5717239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kybard" >Kybard</a></span></li> <li><em>Hurts to talk. Please. Hard to tal— (video ends)</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 November 2019 - selected by <em>PrLosash</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4204">SCP-4204</a> (To Pluck the Moon From the Sky) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5549954&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Dyslexion" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5549954)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" >Dyslexion</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4204 was discovered when a person attempting to break into Fort Knox failed to exit the vault before sunrise.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 November 2019 - selected by <em>Vincent Van Gone</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4428">Dr. Michaels</a> (Dr. Michaels is not in danger.) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5190300&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Henzoid" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5190300)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" >Henzoid</a></span></li> <li><em>DOMC NOTICE: This file requires non-anomalous comprehensive inoculation.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 November 2019 - selected by <em>Dyslexion</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4608">SCP-4608</a> (Appleseed) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span></li> <li><em>Engraved on approximately 75% of trees within SCP-4608 were thaumaturgic sigils and symbols relating to Norse mythology.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">December 2019:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 December 2019 - selected by <em>gee0765</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4677">SCP-4677</a> (Coke, Cow, and Capitalism) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4677-1 is a 100-page document detailing the Coca-Cola original formula and the four rituals required to produce it.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 December 2019 - selected by <em>cybersqyd</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/adoption-poster-darius">Adoption Poster: Darius!</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span></li> <li><em>I can get pretty loud if someone I don't like comes near, so be careful!</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 December 2019 - selected by <em>RockTeethMothEyes</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/weissman-model-assistance-clones">'Weissman Model Assistance Clones' (ET796/IH249/W3336)</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3213383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="OthellotheCat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3213383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" >OthellotheCat</a></span></li> <li><em>Be in the best hands in your twilight years.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 December 2019 - selected by <em>Simartar</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/a-clean-fast-end">A Clean, Fast End</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simartar" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5489226&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Simartar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5489226)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simartar" >Simartar</a></span></li> <li><em>If there are seven-year-old gala posters up, the chances of the site being operational are slim at best.</em></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2020&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;JANUARY&nbsp;-&nbsp;APRIL</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2020&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;JANUARY&nbsp;-&nbsp;APRIL&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">January 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 January 2020 - selected by <em>TheMightyMcB</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2410">SCP-2410</a> (We Are Beary Sorry) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" >TheMightyMcB</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5028224&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Crashington" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5028224)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" >Crashington</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4463776&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="N_Aepic_Fael" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4463776)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" >N_Aepic_Fael</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-2410 refers to stuffed bears that have experienced an ectoentropic phenomenon…</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 January 2020 - selected by <em>Francis Scalia</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4755">SCP-4755</a> (When We Are Omnipotent) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" >Nagiros</a></span></li> <li><em>The following anomaly is Level 6/4755 classified.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 January 2020 - selected by <em>Kilonova</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4823">SCP-4823</a> (The Whole World Has Gone Bananas!) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sebarus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2341265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Sebarus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2341265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sebarus" >Sebarus</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4823 is a ripe specimen of Musa acuminata, more commonly known as a Cavendish banana.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 January 2020 - selected by <em>Cerastes</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/sometimes-it-s-not-funny">Sometimes It's Not Funny</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1345012&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="kinchtheknifeblade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1345012)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" >kinchtheknifeblade</a></span></li> <li><em>jockjamsvol6: Guys, I got some bad news.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">February 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 February 2020 - selected by <em>cybersqyd</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/ambrose-backdoor-soho">Ambrose Backdoor Soho</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="UraniumEmpire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" >UraniumEmpire</a></span></li> <li><em>Ambrose is proud to present Ambrose BackDoor SoHo, a unique blend of contemporary art and fine dining experiences.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 February 2020 - selected by <em>MalyceGraves</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4372">SCP-4372</a> (So Very Small, So Very Safe) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/francis-scalia" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=209952&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Francis Scalia" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=209952)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/francis-scalia" >Francis Scalia</a></span></li> <li><em>Due to these compression effects, the internal topography of SCP-4372 appears vastly larger than its outer dimensions.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 February 2020 - selected by <em>F15H35</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4438">SCP-4438</a> (FOURTH) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" >Tanhony</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4438 is a rare phenomena which is known to occur when an individual is making a choice between three similar objects or entities.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 February 2020 - selected by <em>gee0765</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4357">SCP-4357</a> (Slimelord) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/literallymechanical" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2829014&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="LiterallyMechanical" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2829014)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/literallymechanical" >LiterallyMechanical</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4357-0-A: OH MY GOD, RUDY, LEARN TO READ SARCASM. I WAS JUST MOCKING YOU.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">March 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 March 2020 - selected by <em>N_Aepic_Fael</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5621">SCP-5621</a> (Jealousy, Murder, and Alchemy) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=318209&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="DrMagnus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=318209)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" >DrMagnus</a></span></li> <li><em>Due to the immobile nature of SCP-5621, the pool complex at Calvin University is marked as closed at this time.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 March 2020 - selected by <em>RockTeethMothEyes</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4236">SCP-4236</a> (It's the End of the World (And Everyone Feels Fine)) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/legotrekker" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5505138&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Legotrekker" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5505138)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/legotrekker" >Legotrekker</a></span></li> <li><em>&quot;It doesn't really matter anymore anyway. The hype is gone, the movement is over.&quot;</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 March 2020 - selected by <em>DrUnoriginal</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4192">SCP-4192</a> (As Above) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/connor-macwarren" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3741977&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Connor MacWarren" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3741977)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/connor-macwarren" >Connor MacWarren</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4192 refers to the nucleus of a single Hydrogen atom that emits radio waves at random intervals.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 March 2020 - selected by <em>HammerMaiden</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4197">SCP-4197</a> (Hollow) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5549954&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Dyslexion" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5549954)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" >Dyslexion</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4197 is a thirty-two-year-old adult humanoid female named Doctor Sarah Veers, an acclaimed surgeon and known practitioner of cytomancy.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">April 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 April 2020 - selected by <em>Zoobeeny</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5908">SCP-5908</a> (Missing Bullets) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-5908 was designed with thaumaturgic runes along the barrel capable of triggering a ritual upon firing of the weapon.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 April 2020 - selected by <em>barredowl</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4529">SCP-4529</a> (A Walk in the Park) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/barredowl" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6001754&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="barredowl" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6001754)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/barredowl" >barredowl</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4529 is a forest neighboring the playground of Herbert Baker Elementary School, situated in Edmonton, AB, Canada.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 April 2020 - selected by <em>Dr Sage Evergreen</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5199">SCP-5199</a> (I Always Loved You, Dear, and I Always Will.) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/notochordian" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4940522&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Notochordian" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4940522)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/notochordian" >Notochordian</a></span></li> <li><em>Both components of SCP-5199 were brought into containment on May 5th, 2019, shortly after the surgical removal of SCP-5199-A.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 April 2020 - selected by <em>Sonderance</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4645">SCP-4645</a> (Blackmailing Computer) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Calibri Bold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" >Calibri Bold</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4645 is also capable of targeting individuals with threats; however, its influence has not been seen to extend beyond Site-15.</em></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <p>~</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2020&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;MAY&nbsp;-&nbsp;AUGUST</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2020&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;MAY&nbsp;-&nbsp;AUGUST&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">May 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 May 2020 - selected by <em>Calibri Bold</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4456">SCP-4456-D</a> (No One Expects The Spanish Decommission!) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Calibri Bold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" >Calibri Bold</a></span></li> <li><em>After every reproduction incident, the new SCP-4456 instance is to be provided with 2,500 pounds of pure silver.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 May 2020 - selected by <em>Nagiros</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4310">SCP-4310</a> (The Hero's Journey) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" >A Random Day</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" >The Great Hippo</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4310 is an anomalous species of centipede.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 May 2020 - selected by <em>cybersqyd</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/the-eschaton">Serpent Bound \\\ BEAR WITNESS</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" >Nagiros</a></span></li> <li><em>The Eschaton is self-evident.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 May 2020 - selected by <em>RockTeethMothEyes</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3520">SCP-3520</a> (Fourteen Orangutans) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2527320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="LordStonefish" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2527320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" >LordStonefish</a></span></li> <li><em>Despite apparent ease of containment, reclassification to Keter is under possible consideration.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">June 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 June 2020 - selected by <em>sirpudding</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2656">SCP-2656</a> (The Idiot Box) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cupertinoeffect" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1560371&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="CupertinoEffect" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1560371)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cupertinoeffect" >CupertinoEffect</a></span></li> <li><em>Stage 4: Sections of the brain are further dissected.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 June 2020 - selected by <em>DianaBerry</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5553">SCP-5553</a> (Psycho Social Media) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/citytoast" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372124&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="CityToast" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372124)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/citytoast" >CityToast</a></span></li> <li><em>Premature shutdown of the device does not mitigate the lethal effect of the infohazard.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 June 2020 - selected by <em>Naveil</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5909">SCP-5909</a> (The Endless Shrimp) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-5909 is a crustacean measuring an estimated 2.1 light-years in length, located 7.5 light-years from the Sol System.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 June 2020 - selected by <em>Zoobeeny</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/the-seed-of-an-idea">The Seed of an Idea</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedeadlymoose" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=732274&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="thedeadlymoose" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=732274)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedeadlymoose" >thedeadlymoose</a></span></li> <li><em>&quot;Not Pandora's Box,&quot; Suit said. &quot;Let's call it what it is.&quot;</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">July 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 July 2020 - selected by <em>OCuin</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3385">SCP-3385</a> (The Last Voyage of the <em>Far Horizon</em>.) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-3385 is a retrofitted</em> Vanguard<em>-class nuclear powered submersible vehicle.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>1 July 2020 - selected by <em>caspian2</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5440">SCP-5440</a> (Hotline Moses) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-5440 caused the bush to spontaneously combust and remain burning for approximately two and a half hours.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 July 2020 - selected by <em>Captain Cold</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5545">SCP-5545</a> (𝙰 𝙱 𝙽 𝙾 𝚁 𝙼 𝙰 𝙻 𝙸 𝚃 𝚈) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2199269&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Yossipossi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2199269)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" >Yossipossi</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Calibri Bold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" >Calibri Bold</a></span></li> <li><em>Conceptual Site-344-2 contains SCP-5545-2 via association lock.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 July 2020 - selected by <em>REDESERT</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5898">SCP-5898</a> (Corn Belt) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/its-a-bad-idea" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3181609&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Its a Bad Idea" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3181609)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/its-a-bad-idea" >Its a Bad Idea</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ohnonium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6050049&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Ohnonium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6050049)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ohnonium" >Ohnonium</a></span></li> <li><em><strong>Update 13/01/2020:</strong> Under no circumstances should Barn-002 be left unattended.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">August 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 August 2020 - selected by <em>Riemann</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3393-ex">SCP-3393-EX</a> (Girlfriend) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span></li> <li><em>Dr. Rivera is unable to retain knowledge regarding Dr. Verity or perceive him when directly confronted.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 August 2020 - selected by <em>forbiddenquest</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/mission-accomplished">Mission Accomplished</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weizhong" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1777811&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="weizhong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1777811)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weizhong" >weizhong</a></span></li> <li><em>Well. No other way around it, he supposed.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 August 2020 - selected by <em>Sonderance</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5785">SCP-5785</a> (Craptivism) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/deadly-bread" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3988532&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Deadly Bread" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3988532)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/deadly-bread" >Deadly Bread</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sonderance" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6091992&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Sonderance" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6091992)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sonderance" >Sonderance</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-5785 is capable of manifesting two connected portals of equal size with the sole limitation that one portal must be located within its body.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 August 2020 - selected by <em>cybersqyd</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/project-proposal-1994-103">Project Proposal 1994-103: &quot;A Song of Hope and Home&quot;</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" >stormbreath</a></span></li> <li><em>A listener that listens to the entirety of the song will experience a vision of my journey to the most beautiful thing that I have ever seen.</em></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <p>~</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2020&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;SEPTEMBER&nbsp;-&nbsp;DECEMBER</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2020&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;SEPTEMBER&nbsp;-&nbsp;DECEMBER&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">September 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 September 2020 - selected by <em>KaraKatt</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5380">SCP-5380</a> (My World) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6394107&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="chiifu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6394107)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" >chiifu</a></span></li> <li><em>I hope you'll live a good life. I'm sorry I couldn't be with you more.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 September 2020 - selected by <em>REDESERT</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5595">SCP-5595</a> (Geoffrey Quincy Harrison the Third: Site-Director, Gumball Machine) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguepjp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5813664&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="PlaguePJP" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5813664)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguepjp" >PlaguePJP</a></span></li> <li><em>PLEASE BRING ME TO MY OFFICE. DR. CROIX IS HOSTING A MUTINY.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 September 2020 - selected by <em>Naveil</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/i-just-wanna-survive">I Don't Wanna Be Special (I Just Wanna Survive)</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oboebandgeek99" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1782920&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Oboebandgeek99" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1782920)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oboebandgeek99" >Oboebandgeek99</a></span></li> <li><em>It's Eric, by the way, in case you've forgotten. My therapist is making me do this.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 September 2020 - selected by <em>Francis Scalia</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5335">SCP-5335</a> (The Freudian Split) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-5335 was originally a highly decorated Special Agent with the FBI: Unusual Incidents Unit.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">October 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 October 2020 - selected by <em>Cerastes</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5462">SCP-5462</a> (Misery is the State of Every Soul Burdened by Mortality.) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cerastes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3352053&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Cerastes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3352053)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cerastes" >Cerastes</a></span></li> <li><em>[…] commonly referred to as his Black Paintings due to their emotionally disturbing contents, themes, and use of dark colours.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 October 2020 - selected by <em>Grigori Karpin</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5456">SCP-5456</a> (Sweatmother) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/faminepulse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4275444&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="faminepulse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4275444)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/faminepulse" >faminepulse</a></span></li> <li><em>“We can be human, yeah we can be respectful, but we can't tolerate chaos. You</em> have <em>to be our<sup>[sic]</sup> own dads.”</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 October 2020 - selected by <em>Sonderance</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4423">SCP-4423</a> (StepDemon) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5549954&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Dyslexion" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5549954)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" >Dyslexion</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4423 is a Tartarean-Class demonic entity that manifests during sleep paralysis.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 October 2020 - selected by <em>OCuin</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5788">SCP-5788</a> (Partners in sync) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1787775&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Riemann" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1787775)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" >Riemann</a></span></li> <li><em>The integration of SCP-5788 into the plumbing of the kitchen makes removal and characterisation difficult.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">November 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 November 2020 - selected by <em>cybersqyd</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/they-call-him-he-who-cannot-see-his-reflection">To The Dreams He Is No Nobody</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" >SoullessSingularity</a></span></li> <li><em>Suffice to say, Nobody and the dreams have something that humans may identify as a friendship.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 November 2020 - selected by <em>Dr Moned</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/catching-up">Catching Up</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4558017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Grigori Karpin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4558017)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" >Grigori Karpin</a></span></li> <li><em>“I know you and a group of MTF-Beta-777 went into an alternate reality. You ‘read’ a structure there and had what amounts to a psychotic break.”</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 November 2020 - selected by <em>Truc Linh</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/procedure-420-perinaldo">Procedure 420-Perinaldo</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppermint-legos" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5515758&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="peppermint_legos" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5515758)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppermint-legos" >peppermint_legos</a></span></li> <li><em>My grandpa dodged Vietnam with a bari sax.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 November 2020 - selected by <em>caspian2</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5610">SCP-5610</a> (To Put a Cat on Your Head) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6030962&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Veralta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6030962)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" >Veralta</a></span></li> <li><em>Approximately 56 percent of Japan's population has been found to have an instance of SCP-5610 resting atop of their head.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">December 2020:</span></span></h4> <p>No Reviewers' Spotlight features this month due to contest prize feature schedule. Happy Holidays!</p> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2021&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;JANUARY&nbsp;-&nbsp;APRIL</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2021&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;JANUARY&nbsp;-&nbsp;APRIL&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">January 2021:</span></span></h4> <p>Double Reviewers’ Spotlight features this month due to contest prize feature schedule!</p> <p><strong>1 January 2021 - selected by <em>TheAlienBaby</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4333">SCP-4333</a> (The Profligate) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" >CadaverCommander</a></span></li> <li><em>SCP-4333's behavior is distinguished by its primary anomalous property, which allows it to spontaneously manifest currency.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>1 January 2021 - selected by <em>cybersqyd</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/penny-for-your-thoughts">Penny for Your Thoughts?</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4057128&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Alces_alces" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4057128)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" >Alces_alces</a></span></li> <li><em>&quot;Heads I tell them, tails I don't.&quot;</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 January 2021 - selected by <em>Nagiros</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5699">SCP-5699</a> (Take Care of Yourself.) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/amelia-wright" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3754950&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Amelia Wright" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3754950)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/amelia-wright" >Amelia Wright</a></span></li> <li><em>As such, the O5 Council have ruled that SCP-5699 does not require active containment.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 January 2021 - selected by <em>Quadraginta</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5266">SCP-5266</a> (IDIOT SUCCUMBS TO NEUROTOXIN WHILE LISTENING TO MACHO MAN CLICK NOW TO SEE) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iamtheooga" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3942052&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="IAmTheOoga" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3942052)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iamtheooga" >IAmTheOoga</a></span></li> <li><em>Object Class: Keter</em></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224185" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
